<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Ultra Skool', description: 'Advanced consciousness engineering with immersive modules, research, and workshop access.' }) %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="main-page">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <section class="hero-shell">
                <div class="page-orb left-[-5rem] top-10 h-44 w-44 bg-purple-500/18"></div>
                <div class="page-orb bottom-[-6rem] right-[-3rem] h-64 w-64 bg-fuchsia-500/12"></div>

                <div class="relative z-10 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:items-center">
                    <div>
                        <span class="style-kicker mb-6">Ultra Skool</span>
                        <h1 class="title mb-5">Advanced Consciousness Engineering</h1>
                        <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-[#e0e0ff]/84 md:text-xl">
                            Welcome to the frontier of consciousness exploration. Ultra Skool represents the convergence of cutting-edge ultrasound technology and quantum biology, where we delve deep into the very fabric of consciousness itself.
                        </p>

                        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                            <span class="style-chip">Ultrasound stimulation</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Microtubule theory</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Quantum biology</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Collective exploration</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
                            <div class="style-metric">
                                <p class="section-label">Focus</p>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-white">Explore protocols, theory, and real-time experimentation with a clearer structure.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="style-metric">
                                <p class="section-label">Access</p>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-white">Join the Skool community, dive into modules, and attend live workshop sessions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="video-shell">
                        <div class="relative h-0 overflow-hidden rounded-[1.25rem] pb-[56.25%]">
                            <iframe
                                class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-full"
                                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kozJJDl8nJ0?si=vJKEXayc3p_hNMx1"
                                title="Ultra Skool introduction"
                                frameborder="0"
                                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                                allowfullscreen>
                            </iframe>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
                <article class="section-shell">
                    <p class="section-label">Inside the experience</p>
                    <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-lg text-white">Master advanced ultrasound stimulation techniques.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-lg text-white">Explore microtubule consciousness theory.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-lg text-white">Access quantum-level brain states.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-lg text-white">Pioneer new frontiers in mind enhancement.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-lg italic text-purple-300/90">
                        Drawing from Dr. Stuart Hameroff's groundbreaking research, we explore the profound connection between consciousness and quantum processes within neural microtubules. Through advanced ultrasound stimulation and xenon-enhanced protocols, we're opening new pathways to deeper states of awareness.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <aside class="section-shell text-center">
                    <p class="section-label">Limited access window</p>
                    <p class="mt-4 font-cormorant text-3xl text-white md:text-4xl">Enter while the portal is open.</p>
                    <div id="countdown" class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4">
                        <div class="style-metric min-w-[110px]">
                            <span id="minutes" class="block text-4xl font-semibold text-purple-300 md:text-5xl">05</span>
                            <span class="mt-2 block text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#e0e0ff]/65">Minutes</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-metric min-w-[110px]">
                            <span id="seconds" class="block text-4xl font-semibold text-purple-300 md:text-5xl">00</span>
                            <span class="mt-2 block text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#e0e0ff]/65">Seconds</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
                        <button id="cta-button" class="quantum-button w-full">
                            Enter Ultra Skool Now
                        </button>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#d9d2fb]/76">Join the advanced consciousness engineering collective at Skool.com/ultra.</p>
                        <p class="text-sm italic text-purple-300/82">Explore unprecedented modules in quantum consciousness expansion.</p>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 